channel.title: Intro to Hyperthyroidism and Graves Disease
channel.description: Hyperthyroidism and Graves Disease are complicated and under-researched diseases. This set of podcasts gives a good intro to the topics and points of contention.

item.title: 1: Kimberly Dorris - A Comprehensive Analysis of Graves' Disease
item.description: This episode is a thorough presentation of Graves' Disease from Kimberly Dorris, an educator and expert, and also a patient. In this episode, listeners will gain a thorough understanding of a disease that is often confused with other diagnosis.
